README
This is my third map uploaded to FPS Banana. Let me know of any glitches/bugs/exploits you can find (if any) by emailing me 

at hjhkbn@gmail.com or by leaving a comment.

INSTALLATION
Just extract the map to your cstrike/maps folder. Usually its C:/Program Files/Steam/steamapps/(your username)/counter-

stirke source/cstrike/maps.

There are nine traps in all, ranging from trap floors to spikes impaling whoever is unfortunate enough to be ensnared by 

their vicious grip. DOWNLOAD MY OTHER MAPS TOO!
